    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I'm parting with this absolute beauty and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been pampered since day one\u2014seriously, there's not a single scratch or blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior is so clean it still smells brand new. If you've been looking for a car that's in truly flawless shape, you've found it. Treat yourself to a test drive and see why I'm so excited about this one!",
      "price": 44900.0,
