      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this chassis is flawless: the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure peak timing precision. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with no bushing degradation. Finished in its original paint with a flawless interior, this M3 represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning purist.",
